  "section_title": "Ashta Veerattam Thalangal",
  "section_text": "Further information : Category : Ashta Veeratta Stalam The temples where Lord Shiva is believed to have performed with fury . The eight temples are in 1 . Thiruvadhikai 2 . Thirukoyilur 3 . Thirukkadayur 4 . Vazhoovur 5 . Thirukkurakaval ( kurukkai ) 6 . Thiruppaliyalur 7 . Thirukandiyur 8 . Thiruvirkudi .",
  "uid": "Paadal_Petra_Sthalam_2",
  "intro": "The Paadal Petra Thalam are 275 temples that are revered in the verses of Saiva Nayanars in the 6th-9th century CE and are amongst the greatest Shiva temples of the continent. The Divya Desams by comparison are the 108 Vishnu temples glorified in the poems of the contemporary Vaishnava Alvars of Tamil Nadu, India"
}